{"tid":2140888,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"山友藏摺刀雷射筆脫罪 官指無證據證明有意圖傷人","createTime":"2020-08-05T09:48:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T11:23:29.000Z","uid":56115,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c071a6fef51570a67b311c907a32f45cc0a5ea88","tid":2140888,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:48:48.000Z","msg":"為慶祝國慶而身穿紅衣的婦人，稱去年10月2日深夜在將軍澳港鐵站遭人圍攻，被搶電話、遭淋水、噴漆及以雨傘襲擊。警員凌晨時分在區內截查28歲售貨員，從其腰包內搜出一把摺刀及雷射筆，控以在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪。案件早前審訊，裁判官梁少玲今裁決指，無證據證明被告與婦人遇襲案有關；縱使被告管有雷射筆等行為可疑，但控方指控不具體，<span class=\"red\">未能證明被告管有物品的意圖是用作傷人，裁定他罪名不成立。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/NVYJTOYCTMQMV7EPEHW2DL6QLI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2FNVYJTOYCTMQMV7EPEHW2DL6QLI%2F&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeaojsSVnKafjD5u%2BKhFsBKzQ%3D&h=5a8b5b74\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2FNVYJTOYCTMQMV7EPEHW2DL6QLI%2F&h=41101711\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/NVYJTOYCTMQMV7EPEHW2DL6QLI/</a>"},{"pid":"cd9c613f845a353405de9e4ab2af49940c1e05f4","tid":2140888,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:49:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e1a92bc050efdfaea122cedda97ed4dc4960116","tid":2140888,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:51:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098140816b07ea3e4d98c3374313d7c273ade653","tid":2140888,"uid":37869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:52:57.000Z","msg":"見到某d法官就知道罪名一定成立<br />\n見到罪名不成立就知一定唔係某d法官"},{"pid":"d10bf8a87fbc45983f945bf0df6b63b69c5c734a","tid":2140888,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.g